FCL Components printers' printer line-up;
Print Mechanisms, Label Printers, Ticket Printers, POS printers, Mobile Printers and Dot Matrix Printers.

CFD SEMI has been founded on more than two decades of professional experience in IT and CFD. These two pillars denote:
- DCD's SEMI innovative approach in chip design like e.g. World's Fastest 8051 CPU, fully scalable 32-bit CPU and 100% safe cryptographic system
- CFD scientists well known for customized CFD solutions like Applied Mathematical Modelling,, Chemical Engineering etc.

We believe that the power of innovation opens a brave new world for everyone. That's why we decided to design a fully scalable hardware accelerator (ASIC) for Computational Fluid Dynamics with an algorithm based on the high-order Discontinuous Galerkin method. Our technology is a breakthrough available for every single engineer and company:
- LES available for every CFD engineer;
- reducing computation time;
- the high order computation method;
- money savings in the purchase of a new computational equipment;
- less power consumption.

Ресурс-Медиа – один из мощнейших широкопрофильных ИТ-дистрибьюторов, с широким набором прямых контрактов крупнейших вендоров и склады в 21 городе России.
На рынке :
• Крупнейший на рынке расходных материалов для печатной техники.
• В тройке крупнейших на рынке устройств печати.
• Заметный игрок на рынке мониторов, ноутбуков и носителей информации.

В ассортименте: расходные материалы, оргтехника (принтеры, МФУ, сканеры, факсы, плоттеры), ноутбуки, мониторы, планшеты, проекторы, аксессуары, офисное оборудование, носители информации, товары для сервис-центров .

Высочайшее качество  оригинальной продукции от ведущих мировых производителей. Среди них: A-Data, Acer, Asus, Apacer, AQC, BenQ, Brother, Canon, Cisco, Defender, D-Link, EMTEC (BASF), Epson, Fellowes, G-Form, Gigaset, HP, HSM, Katun, Kingston, Konica Minolta, KYOCERA Document Solutions, Lasting Impressions, Lenovo, Lexmark, LG, Lomond, Microsoft, NEC, Netis, Oce, Office Kit, OKI, Optoma, Oxion, Panasonic, Ricoh, Philips, Sagemcom, Samsung, SanDisk, Screen Media, Seagate, Silicon Power, Sony, Static Control, Sharp, Synology, TDK, Toshiba, TP-LINK, Transcend, UniNet, Verbatim, ViewSonic, Western Digital, Xerox, ZyXEL. 
На складах Ресурс-Медиа реально находится более 20 000 номенклатурных позиций! 

Ресурс-Медиа развивается! 
Работая с нами, вы обретаете следующие преимущества:
• конкурентные цены; 
• широкий ассортимент и постоянное наличие продукции на складе; 
• возможности доставки по Москве до склада партнера или транспортной компании; 
• оперативная информационная поддержка: ежедневные электронные рассылки (новости о продукции, ценах, программах), периодические рассылки печатных материалов и электронных носителей; 
• партнерский В2В сайт;
• маркетинговые программы, бонусные программы, программы авторизации, возможность путешествовать; 
• внимание и поддержку профессиональных менеджеров;
• удобный сервис: широкий ассортимент  продукции Ресурс-Медиа доступен со складов 20 регионов страны.

Orbit strives to be the best distributor in the world through stronger partnerships with Customers and Suppliers, and responsiveness to their immediate and long-term requirements; 
Promote our Quality Management System in order to enhance Customer Satisfaction and have a better understanding of –and compliance by–our Suppliers;
- Work closely with our Vendors to establish the highest Quality standards;
- Train our staff in the needs and responsibilities of Quality Management;
- Follow a concept of Continual Improvement and make best use of our management resources in all Quality matters.
- Orbit emerged from over 20 years of direct business-to-business experience in the technology industry with a customer focused approach and zero tolerance policy for mistakes. With our solid background in the OEM culture where one small error can be costly, adhere to the strictest Quality Management Systems, and we understand how supply chain management decisions impact customer values. We carry those years of tradition in our day-to-day business attitude whether our products end up in a factory shop floor, a production house, or your living room. Care and attention to detail are our hallmark.
Our factory direct relations bring a breadth of knowledge on the latest and the greatest in Computers; including Desktops, Laptops, Netbooks & Notebooks, Electronic Components like Motherboards, CPUs ,Memory / RAM, Hard Drives, Wireless Input Devices (Keyboard / Mice) , Barebone Systems & Kits, Cameras & Camcorders, Gaming Devices, Televisions (LCD TVs / HDTV / Plasma), all types of GPS Navigation devices, Accessories and much more. We bring you the products you want, with the performance you need, and quality you deserve at the right value. Our team of dedicated professionals and our worldwide network makes it possible for you to shop OrbitDirect with ease, and confidence – We Orbit the globe to find the technological solutions you need, and products you want – At prices YOU can afford
